## Tell me again, say again; {{non-gloss definition|used in asking a question to which one may have already received the answer, but cannot remember it.}}
##: ''What's that called, '''again'''?''
## I ask again, I say again; {{non-gloss definition|used in repeating a question or statement.}}
##: '''''Again''', as I said before, I'm not criticizing, I just want to understand.''
## Here too, here also, in this case as well; {{non-gloss definition|used in applying a previously made point to a new instance; sometimes preceded by "here".}}
##: ''Approach B is better than approach A in many respects, but '''again''', there are implementation difficulties in implementing it.''

